import Title from "./component/Title"
    import {Navbar, Nav, Button,Form,FormControl} from "react-bootstrap"

    const SubNavbar = () => {

        return  <>

                <Navbar bg="primary" variant="dark" className="mt-5 w-50 mx-auto">

                <Navbar.Brand href="#home">
                    <Title></Title>
                </Navbar.Brand>

                <Navbar.Collapse id="navbarScroll">

                <Form className="d-flex">

                    <FormControl
                      type="search"
                      placeholder="Search"
                      className="me-2"
                      aria-label="Search"
                    />

                    <Button variant="outline-success" className="btn btn-succ">Search</Button>

                </Form>    

                <Nav className="ms-auto">

                    <Nav.Link href="/profile">
                        <Button type="button" className="btn btn-light btn-md ">Find friends</Button>
                    </Nav.Link>

                    <Nav.Link href="/profile">
                        <Button type="button" className="btn btn-light btn-md ">Friend requests</Button>
                    </Nav.Link>

                </Nav>

                </Navbar.Collapse>

                </Navbar>
    
                </>
     }

     export default SubNavbar
